Priscilla Morrill https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Priscilla_Morrill 0 Priscilla Alden Morrill (June 4, 1927 – November 9, 1994) was an American actress. She is best known for playing Edie Grant on the successful sitcom The Mary Tyler Moore Show in 1973 and 1975. Priscilla_Alden_Morrill ( June_4_,_1927 – November_9_,_1994 ) was an_American_actress . She is_best_known for playing Edie_Grant on the_successful_sitcom The_Mary_Tyler_Moore_Show in 1973_and_1975 .
